dc_title_s: South America, French Guiana and Brazil, Cayenne to Cabo Orange (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From various sources to 1996." Includes source diagram. Map no.24350. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
